id\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andria\"}, {\"begin\": 766, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bain_Capital\", \"score\": 0.9999999935948836, \"rank\": 6.383517838527674e-09, \"text\": \"Bain\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bain_Capital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bain_Capital\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Is that the can opener?\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What is happening here?\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the bigger problem here is that we were looking at these athletes and we were marvelling like, look how big, look how strong.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 986, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We saw every type of body type, we saw incredible physical feats and then this woman came out and she made us feel like, I guess we are all Olympians, right?\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because we can all get down on the floor and do weird stuff and pretend to yawn.\\\"\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn was on Wednesday morning notably absent from the line-up of notable Olympic athletes who touched down in Sydney from Paris via Perth after the Games.\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1232, \"end\": 1236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9582465855258101, \"rank\": 0.0331190361458736, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1342, \"end\": 1348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9995706630098917, \"rank\": 0.00034356353929859755, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"ht