pe with her husband Samuel Free and her parents, according to 2GB.\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1645, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes after World DanceSport Federation (WDSF) secretary Sergei Nifontov said the 36-year-old was offered mental health support due to some of the reactions to her performance.\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1691, \"end\": 1695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said the WDSF had been in direct contact with Gunn and Australian Olympic team officials to offer her support from a safeguarding officer.\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 1877, \"end\": 1881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9582465855258101, \"rank\": 0.0331190361458736, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1886, \"end\": 1909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999777498945, \"rank\": 2.2250172182096307e-08, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are aware ab